descriptor.name: Chicco Sensitive Baby Laundry Detergent - Fresh Spring, Removes Tough Stains & Odour, 500 ml
descriptor.short_desc: Chicco Sensitive Baby Laundry Detergent - Fresh Spring, Removes Tough Stains & Odour
descriptor.long_desc: Chicco Baby Laundry Detergent has been specially formulated to effectively clean baby’s clothes by removing tough stains, odours, and germs while keeping them gentle and delicate on baby’s skin- a preferred choice for both parents and baby. It has a unique combination of 5 key enzymes working on different stains and germs on the clothes such as baby food, ghee-oil, fruits-vegetables, dirt-dust, and pee-poop. The Chicco baby laundry detergent gives your little one’s clothes a complete hygienic wash with antibacterial and antifungal properties, killing 99% of the germs present on the clothes. It is dermatologically tested and found to be 100% safe on the baby's tender skin.

descriptor.name: Chicco Strawberry Flavour Toothpaste For Babies, 50 g
descriptor.short_desc: Chicco Strawberry Flavour Toothpaste For Babies
descriptor.long_desc:
At the early age of growth, a baby’s teeth are very sensitive and can get permanently damaged if not taken care of properly. Chicco fluoride-free, preservative-free toothpaste is specially formulated for babies’ milk teeth to clean and sanitize them but with extra care and protection. The bio-available calcium and xylitol present in toothpaste work to strengthen the baby’s teeth and prevent cavities. The toothpaste is very low on REA (Relative Enamel Abrasivity) level which indicates that it protects the baby’s gentle and soft tooth enamel from damage and keeps them safe. No preservatives and SLS in the formula make it safe for babies.

Chicco offers the right flavours for the right age of babies for faster adaptation to their taste buds as babies taste buds recognize these flavour since early ages as they are given mashed fruits in the early days of life.

descriptor.name: Chicco 3 in 1 Baby Bottle Sterilizer for 6 Bottles, Fast and Effective Sterilization for Nipples and Accessories, Auto Shut Off, White
descriptor.short_desc: Chicco 3 in 1 Baby Bottle Sterilizer for 6 Bottles, Fast and Effective Sterilization for Nipples and Accessories
descriptor.long_desc:
Chicco Sterilizer 3 in 1 helps in simplifying mothers’ daily practice of sterilization and eliminates germs naturally, safely and effectively with the help of steam
Effective Sterilization: Eliminates 99.9% harmful household germs resulting in effective sterilization
24-hour Protection: Keeps the bottles/objects sterilized for up to 24 hours till the time lid is closed
Adjustable and Slim: Provides an option to choose from 3 different configuration: full size (6 bottles), compact (2 bottles) and microwave (2 bottles) based on the number of objects/items to be sterilized
Compact Eco and Fast Sterilization: Fast and easy to use, sterilizes in just 5 minutes (warming time excluded) while also offering an advantage to carry along while travelling. Also, allows saving up to 25% of time and energy
Automatic Safe Stop: Switches off automatically at the end of the cycle
The steps of sterilization are so simple that even when the mother is not at home, anybody can manage it in her absence
Sterilizer works on the process of intense steam that effectively cleans the baby utensils without affecting the product quality
Chicco is one of the largest baby care brands in the world. With experience of over 60 years, it offers a wide range of baby products in nursing, baby toiletries, toys, travel (strollers and car safety seats) and fashion categories

descriptor.name: Chicco Lite Way Stroller with Bumper Bar, Pram for 0-5 Years Baby/Toddler/Kid (Boy,Girl), Fully Reclining Backrest with 4 Positions, Linked Brakes & Shock-Proof Wheels (Upto 22 Kgs, Hydra Aqua Blue)
descriptor.short_desc: The Chicco stroller, Lite Way 4, comes with a foldable umbrella. Users can fold and unfold the umbrella over the stroller according to the requirement. Its canopy is large and extensible to protect the baby from the sun. The handle of this stroller is convenient and easily movable. Parents can quickly move this baby carriage even with one hand. Lite Way 4 stroller is Lightweight and made up of high-quality fabric.
descriptor.long_desc:
The Chicco stroller, Lite Way 4, comes with a foldable umbrella. Users can fold and unfold the umbrella over the stroller according to the requirement. Its canopy is large and extensible to protect the baby from the sun. The handle of this stroller is convenient and easily movable. Parents can quickly move this baby carriage even with one hand. Lite Way 4 stroller is Lightweight and made up of high-quality fabric.
Design of the Lite way 4 stroller: This pram stroller by Chicco has a remarkable style and design for parents and little ones. The modern lines have elegant details. Great attention is given while designing the Lite Way 4 stroller. Its sleek and rigid design makes it unique. Parents will have a sense of satisfaction at just first glance on the Lite Way 4 stroller.
Easy to carry: It is an easily foldable stroller which closes into an umbrella fold. It is easy to carry.
Framework: Lite Way 4 is the perfect combination of elegant design and robust framework. The ideal structure of the Lite Way 4 stroller makes it one of the best strollers available in the market. The stroller is durable and rigid owing to its metallic solid frame.
Light weight: The weight of the stroller is around 7.5Kg. Therefore, it comes under the lightweight category & is easy to carry.
Homologation from birth to 22kgs: The baby stroller can hold weight up to 22Kg. It is one of the highest-weight hold-able strollers available in the market.
Canopy: Lite Way 4 stroller has a canopy over it. The top can be adjusted according to the requirement of the baby and as well as parents. The roof available in the new Chicco stroller is much larger and easily extendable according to the use.
Handle and bumper: There are two separate handles available in the Lite Way 4 stroller. Users can quickly move the stroller either with two hands or with a single hand. The design of the handle looks like the handle of a bicycle. The handle is of the same metallic frame. They are covered with soft cushion pads for the comfort of parents while walking with the stroller. The Chicco stroller is easy to lift even with one hand.

descriptor.short_desc: Chicco Classic Manual Breast Pump - 0m+
descriptor.long_desc: This Chicco Classic Breast Pump is made from high-quality plastic and rubber which is completely safe for you and your little one. This white-coloured breast pump helps in the easy extraction of milk without causing the mother any pain. It comes with a suction rate control system. This advanced system can help regulate the speed of the pump depending on your requirement. This product comes with a comfortable breast shield which helps to extract the milk properly. All the devices that this breast pump kit provides are made of excellent quality material. The breast shield and the feeding bottle can be easily sterilised and cleaned with the help of hot water and a brush. This breast pump kit for nursing moms is an essential device because due to hormonal imbalances some women face problems during lactation.
